It’s hard to know, but here are some things I’d suggest:

  1. Go to AXIS Device Manager | Axis Communications, look for the download link on this page (green button/box), then download and install to be sure you have the latest version;

  2. Upgrade the camera firmware, if needed (see Axis Communications - video player);

  3. Try disabling any firewall (bringing up the driver station should show if anything is enabled);

  4. Reboot computer and power cycle camera.

If none of that helps, posting more about how the camera is connected and maybe a screen shot showing what you are trying to do, and what you are seeing when you try, might help.
